reviewText: not worth buying.  not much eyecandy to see and  no substantial storyline.

Even though the fight scenes are poor, for some reason I still enjoyed this flick. I guess it's because of the lead actress, she's busty and cute. Or maybe because there's sex and nudity in this flick. I don't know.
This product should give age approiate rating for those who like martial arts action films, even c-level films.
